    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vacunauts</strong> 是一款 <strong>混乱的 1-4 人多人合作波防御</strong> 游戏。你和你的星际清洁队被雇佣来 <strong>保护被邪恶的“垃圾叛军”威胁的星球</strong>。你们拥有各种 <strong>有趣的能力</strong>，需要完美地团结在一起（或者混乱地配合）来 <strong>保卫银河系（并获得晋升）</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123790/extras/54fd3624427b080cfb63ba41337e8e56.webp?t=1772203406\" width=616 height=53 /></span>穿上最可爱公司的各种高效员工制服。<strong>与最多 3 位朋友一起在线（待定）或在沙发上聚会</strong>，努力完成你们保卫银河系各个星球的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123790/extras/3e30ae3df0275c26d15e7597c1bef107.poster.avif?t=1772203406\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123790/extras/3e30ae3df0275c26d15e7597c1bef107.webm?t=1772203406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123790/extras/3e30ae3df0275c26d15e7597c1bef107.mp4?t=1772203406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123790/extras/93cce6acbaabf15b53a6cc52dbfd6982.webp?t=1772203406\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>保护</strong> 被入侵的星球，将敌人的力量反击给他们！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索</strong> 各种<strong>不同的能力</strong>并找到你最喜欢的一个。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>堆叠</strong> 这些效果，创造出更强大的 <strong>大规模毁灭性武器</strong>（法律声明：并不是每种组合都能产生大规模毁灭性武器。大规模毁灭性武器的定义因人而异）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>消灭</strong> 各种类型的怪物</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123790/extras/cd9535105bf6b8b98888a39da30d6568.poster.avif?t=1772203406\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123790/extras/cd9535105bf6b8b98888a39da30d6568.webm?t=1772203406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123790/extras/cd9535105bf6b8b98888a39da30d6568.mp4?t=1772203406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多细节敬请期待。</p>",
